---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'How much does this cost?',
    answer:
      'Every project is different. After a discovery call, I\u2019ll put together a proposal with clear pricing based on the scope of work. No surprises.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How long does a typical project take?',
    answer:
      'Most projects move from discovery to launch in 8\u201312 weeks, depending on complexity. We\u2019ll define a realistic timeline together during the scoping phase.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What if I don\u2019t have a technical background?',
    answer:
      'That\u2019s exactly who this service is built for. I handle the technical side and keep you informed in plain language every step of the way.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What do I need to have ready before we start?',
    answer:
      'A clear idea of the problem you\u2019re solving and who you\u2019re solving it for. You don\u2019t need wireframes, specs, or a pitch deck \u2014 we\u2019ll build those together.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Do you build the product yourself or outsource it?',
    answer:
      'I do the work myself. No outsourcing, no hand-offs to junior devs. You get direct access to the person building your product.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What happens after launch?',
    answer:
      'We\u2019ll collect feedback, review metrics, and decide what to improve, add, or cut. Ongoing support and iteration is available as long as you need it.',
  },
];
---

<section class="py-16 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-10">
      Frequently asked questions
    </h2>
    <dl class="space-y-8">
      {
        faqs.map((faq) => (
          <div>
            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">{faq.question}</dt>
            <dd class="text-dark-neutral/80 leading-relaxed">{faq.answer}</dd>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
